      "content": "hey so i need to vent about something weird. i was talking to my landlord today about the rent increase and i could literally feel it in my teeth... like there was this sharp, discordant vibration in his voice when he said the price was fixed. i know it sounds crazy but i can always tell when someone is lying like that. it's like a frequency shift. have you ever heard of anything like that or am i just losing it?",
