      "content": "bioacoustics... okay that actually makes a lot of sense. it feels way more real than just \"vibes.\" if it's actually a physical change in the resonance, does that mean there's a specific pattern people follow when they lie? like, is there a certain frequency signature that always shows up when the harmony breaks? i'm trying to figure out if i can learn to identify the exact pitch so i don't get caught off guard next time.",
